{"tid":1628543,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【裝修佬】手足識自我修正，連衛兵唔使帶風向","createTime":"2019-10-06T03:28:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T07:31:21.000Z","uid":16678,"like":38,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"8b84b4ea390fc4795ddd142fb7fdf48790ee9521","tid":1628543,"uid":16678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:28:11.000Z","msg":"乜鳩都話裝修<br />\n你當手足係你隻卒？<br />\n想入行你就自己出黎<br />\n做多做少手足識自我修正<br />\n我地有獨立思考唔會比人煽動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成個熱門都係傾裝修<br />\n我知好大爭議所以比啲時間手足好無<br />\n仲有新入職裝修佬係咪唔識職安健呀<br />\n得個濕鳩口罩都夠膽出黎行係咪痴撚左線<br />\n搏上鏡定搏炒呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n推十次推返行動 Post<br />\n等陣見<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2857612c155480c89ad9ed72b9ce765b4b149fe8","tid":1628543,"uid":16678,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:29:33.000Z","msg":"推一"},{"pid":"10f65c77044da421b5faeb512f5b94c9248dad00","tid":1628543,"uid":299104,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:29:44.000Z","msg":"講得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N2eJKVS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN2eJKVS.png&h=fd892c2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GobPu5a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGobPu5a.jpg&h=8c19a255&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yYDlCk4w_-I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyYDlCk4w_-I&d=15TDSCYqMG0%2FxcOE0oxfELQTYXQauqfU4Ix09hrgZFI%3D&h=5d7fdbf3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/yYDlCk4w_-I</a>"},{"pid":"f9d7afcbf5201192f002c9c0eda21c479ba95598","tid":1628543,"uid":16678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T03:30